pagination :
1)pagination and sorting is mostly required when we are displaying domain data in tabular formar in UI
2)pagination consists of 2 files->
page size
page no
3)sorting can be done on multiple files in table
4)it is optional hencecan be part of request URL as query parameters

findAll(pagable) findAll(Sort)

this class is extended by JpaRespository so we can directly use its methods
